record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 1649

speaking-unknown-id.title: Ms.
speaking-unknown-id.name: SANDLIN, HERSETH
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to remove the name of Congressman James Moran of Virginia as a cosponsor to H.R. 1649, who was added inadvertently as a cosponsor to that bill.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentlewoman from South Dakota?
